## Typography

Typography style is not based on markup as a general rule, styling fx. articles, extend styling into article style.

Styles for typography is split up into size, weight and family.

<h2 class="fl-text-large">Size</h2>

<div class="fl-text-xx-large">fl-text-xx-large</div>
<div class="fl-text-x-large">fl-text-x-large</div>
<div class="fl-text-large">fl-text-large</div>
<div class="fl-text-medium">fl-text-medium</div>
<div class="fl-text-small">fl-text-small</div>
<div class="fl-text-x-small">fl-text-x-small</div>
<div class="fl-text-xx-small">fl-text-xx-small</div>

{% codeblock %}
	<div class="fl-text-xx-large">fl-text-xx-large</div>
	<div class="fl-text-x-large">fl-text-x-large</div>
	<div class="fl-text-large">fl-text-large</div>
	<div class="fl-text-medium">fl-text-medium</div>
	<div class="fl-text-small">fl-text-small</div>
	<div class="fl-text-x-small">fl-text-x-small</div>
	<div class="fl-text-xx-small">fl-text-xx-small</div>
{% endcodeblock %}

<h2 class="fl-text-large">Weight</h2>

<div class="fl-text-bold">Helvetica neue...</div>
<div class="fl-text-medium">Sofia pro...</div>
<div class="fl-text-regular">Georgia...</div>

{% codeblock %}
