<h2 class="fl-text-large">Colors</h2>

The colors can be used withing style by using sass function `color({colorName})`.

{% sg_color brand fl-color-brand %}
{% sg_color 0 fl-color-0 %}
{% sg_color 50 fl-color-50 %}
{% sg_color 100 fl-color-100 %}
{% sg_color 200 fl-color-200 %}
{% sg_color 300 fl-color-300 %}
{% sg_color 400 fl-color-400 %}
{% sg_color 500 fl-color-500 %}
{% sg_color 600 fl-color-600 %}
{% sg_color 700 fl-color-700 %}
{% sg_color 800 fl-color-800 %}
{% sg_color 900 fl-color-900 %}

<h2 class="fl-text-large">Text colors</h2>

<div class="fl-text-color--brand">fl-text-color--brand</div>
<div class="fl-text-color--0">fl-text-color--0</div>
<div class="fl-text-color--50">fl-text-color--50</div>
<div class="fl-text-color--100">fl-text-color--100</div>
... and so on for all colors

{% codeblock %}
	<div class="fl-text-color--brand">fl-text-color--brand</div>
	<div class="fl-text-color--0">fl-text-color--0</div>
	<div class="fl-text-color--50">fl-text-color--50</div>
	<div class="fl-text-color--100">fl-text-color--100</div>
	... and so on for all colors
{% endcodeblock %}

